#### 创建博客
POST /api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Blog Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first blog post."
}

### 获取博客
GET /api/blogs/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 更新博客
PUT /api/blogs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My Updated Blog Post",
  "content": "This is the updated content of my blog post."
}

#### 删除博客
DELETE /api/blogs/1
Content-Type: application/json
